Package translate

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PreferenceInputTranslator
    Translates preference input of the type (T)CP-nets with unconditional relative importance and CI-nets into models suitable for model checking by (presently) CadenceSMV, NuSMV.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CINetToSMVTranslator
    Translates CI-nets specified in text format into SMV model suitable as input for model checkers Cadence SMV and NuSMV.
    PreferenceInputTranslatorFactory
    Factory class that provides (presently) CINetToSMVTranslator or TCPNetToSMVTranslator implementations
    TCPNetToSMVTranslator
    Translates TCP-nets specified in XML format into SMV model suitable as input for model checkers Cadence SMV and NuSMV.
